Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:35.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}拜託了  Bitter  Tune
